{"tid":255604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母呢個乜撚野港女手勢黎","createTime":"2017-05-24T03:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T04:54:49.000Z","uid":31739,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b086843d5644f2d7676ed3d3345287f4f7230762","tid":255604,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j3z25dsb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj3z25dsb&h=215f8a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老咪碌ig見到好多港女做呢個手勢<br />\n心諗做乜鳩 唔明有咩意思<br />\n咁就問條女到底呢個手勢點解<br />\n佢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:「你咁out架 呢個咪心心嘅手勢」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌你老母 心? 邊撚到心呀? 睇過?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係我理解中 呢個係笑鳩人JJ短嘅手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n港女到底有無腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網查 發現原來又係韓狗野<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jth9xv35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjth9xv35&h=e78e3817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(用頭髮整個屎忽出黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rlvofn58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frlvofn58&h=95c7f53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">邊個同我影相時做個咁嘅手勢我就塞我個心心入你屎眼呀!!!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c4a0de823e0dc41b0e0b5f5c45dbea0cd34ff2fa","tid":255604,"uid":93083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"你out唔out呀？大半年前已經屌緊啦<br />\n又攞出黎呃正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7151dfecbfb74ec463927a21ff4bb2ced6afb6d","tid":255604,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"醒下啦，冇人會同你影相架"},{"pid":"88ed2afd96236333686a9e4cd751dcd0c100f373","tid":255604,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jth9xv35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjth9xv35&h=e78e3817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n果兩條陰想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e2016f784ea2c49c505ede25116f7006c202dc","tid":255604,"uid":9735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"樓主之前衰乜？出返嚟，好重新做人喇"},{"pid":"70dd5d935e9519a21656b365f8885556c797c847","tid":255604,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主之前衰乜？出返嚟，好重新做人喇</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c125d1229d80cec048dbedbca9dd6a2e373312ee","tid":255604,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主之前衰乜？出返嚟，好重新做人喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直無留意韓狗野嘛"},{"pid":"283d891964dc885129735b294faf69fb5c7e284e","tid":255604,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主之前衰乜？出返嚟，好重新做人喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21731d66447650b1b34921432ffbc2cfcc332636","tid":255604,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"韓狗智障風<br />\n中坑唔識正常"},{"pid":"d839c2242f4d59c85f4c25160320ae811a3a8451","tid":255604,"uid":12532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"感覺上有幾年歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2494c67e8c6e94dbae7056749a72638de